{"tid":1528873,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［真心求問］成日話機場係春袋，春喺邊？","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T03:45:09.000Z","uid":13466,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0dd39aa0242cc2b2cd745d18e0d8666aeca807","tid":1528873,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"成日話機場係春袋，之前各區有活動，都有人屌「點解唔入機場？」<br />\n<br />\n總結今日，我真係唔知機場係春乜野袋？<br />\n我更覺今日係捏爆自己春袋多過揸住政府個春袋。<br />\n<br />\n1. 入島塞3個半鐘、出島塞4個鐘（我而家都仲喺巴士未離開到個島），島上手足等支援嘅話，等得嚟比狗溶咗啦！<br />\n<br />\n2. 面對孤島斷交通，今日班狗完全以逸待勞，就玩到班手足要翻山涉水著草咁款。尋日港島開埋鎗，都無今日咁狼狽。<br />\n<br />\n3. 喺出島塞得車嚟，大西北爆晒鑊都番唔到去支援。早知今日唔入機場，留喺大西北支援仲有意義。"},{"pid":"0ad4ea46beddcba1f957f7cd38d673b3e02d2eb7","tid":1528873,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"［分析］如果大家要搞機場見到狗就驚⋯⋯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"18902681964cf8c7e746d8a843842e3e27b42e2a","tid":1528873,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"事實上今日完全俾唔到威脅"},{"pid":"3fd952238ed31d9617165c48ec6e9e837825b4a0","tid":1528873,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"747a8ed47a0e922aae18c49d6db20ea1893b3940","tid":1528873,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:27:37.000Z","msg":"不過冇tg <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804cbf318a74db29317afa86a3d89bf7797de004","tid":1528873,"uid":49016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T1